<p><i><b>Fighting Fantasy</b></i> is a series of single-player fantasy <a href="/wiki/Gamebook" title="Gamebook">gamebooks</a> created by <a href="/wiki/Steve_Jackson_(UK_game_designer)" title="Steve Jackson (UK game designer)">Steve Jackson</a> and <a href="/wiki/Ian_Livingstone" title="Ian Livingstone">Ian Livingstone</a>, originally published by <a href="/wiki/Puffin_Books" title="Puffin Books">Puffin</a> and now by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Wizard_Books&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Wizard Books (page does not exist)">Wizard Books</a>. Although not the first books to use this format, <i>Fighting Fantasy</i> popularised the format and spawned dozens of imitators.</p>
